	<summary>A web app for reading the Bible with full emphasis on the God`s Word only. Sola scriptura</summary>
	<description>
		<p>
			Read the Bible with full emphasis on God's Word only. Sola scriptura. Read God's Word with a deep understanding of His design. Bible elevates your soul with rapid ascending to calm, safety and more.
		</p>
		<p>
			This app is built for reading the Bible on full screen. There is available such features as Bible texts of 28 translations, search, something like bookmarks, reading history, night/light theme, regulation of font size, font-family and some other small nice features. Localization for Українська, Русский, Portuguese and Español.
		</p>
		<p>
			This is FOSS. Here is GitHub -=> https://github.com/Bohooslav/bain.
		</p>
		<p>
			The list of available translations:
		</p>
